<h3>NEED</h3>
<ol>
<li>SEP (significant economic presence = revenue + #users ) and India's right to tax - sovereignty</li>
<li>OECD's [[BEPS]] - inconclusive</li>
<li>Level playing field for digital and brick-mortar</li>
<li>avoid undue power in hands of corporates influencing way of life</li></ol>
<h3>CONCERNS&nbsp;</h3>
<ol>
<li>Retaliatory tariffs from other countries e.g. USA's 301 report</li>
<li>&nbsp;growth of digital companies = hampered</li>
<li>tax passed to customer</li></ol>
<p>WTO in dilemma =&gt; need rules based world order. OECD's BEPS is a good step.&nbsp;</p>
